Mountain View, CA, USA\
94041-2021\
\
I need some help with Firefox or other Mozilla Products.\
The Mozilla community is here to help you. You can search for questions or add a new one: http://support.mozilla.com/en-US/home\
\
What if I change my mind?                \
You can unsubscribe from any Mozilla communications at any time. Please know that your donation is a one-time event, and will not auto-renew.                \
                \
When I Join Mozilla, what happens to my data?\
                \
At the point of signing up your data is being given to Mozilla (which includes the Mozilla Foundation and Corporation). We will never sell, rent, or give your information to any third-party, and will only contact you as part of this program. For more information, check out our terms of service and privacy policy.                \
                \
How will my data be used?\
By signing up for the Join Mozilla program, your data will only be used by Mozilla (and its service providers). You will only receive Mozilla-related information.                \
                \
Help! I have a question about being part of Join Mozilla. Who do I ask?\
Fret not! Just send an e-mail to joinmozilla@mozilla.org and we'll get you sorted out.\
